{"tid":1528472,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[國家恐怖主義] 中央政法委：暴徒躲得過初一　躲不過十五","createTime":"2019-09-01T14:09:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T16:14:24.000Z","uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"16d247fbfab80c26e54dddde7089bd5e49a4d09f","tid":1528472,"uid":53003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:09:05.000Z","msg":"中央政法委微信發表文章，提到香港近日發生暴力事件，指「七勞五傷、玉石俱焚」的香港，美國和歐洲不會心痛，真正為香港心傷的只有中國，受到傷害的是香港的市民。<br />\n<br />\n文章指，想拿香港做文章，要脅中國政府，延緩、阻止甚至中斷中華民族偉大復興的進程，是癡人說夢，恐怖主義手法的暴行嚇不到任何人，反而能讓更多的人看清暴徒的真實嘴臉；街頭暴力不會達到任何目的，只會讓止暴制亂，獲得更加廣泛和堅定的支持。<br />\n<br />\n文章表示，犯下如此暴行，不要再幻想蒙面就能躲得過，俗話說「躲得過初一，躲不過十五」，離月圓之夜還有幾天，暴徒們該自己屈指一算。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478177-20190901.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478177-20190901.htm&d=3Z9ZeYaQzwHPi2iIp4702Cvt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=381675f0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1478177-20190901.htm&h=f95b19e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1478177-20190901.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a00c7cf4098d7e800e8cbed6a4870d6a709a6cfe","tid":1528472,"uid":280058,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:14:32.000Z","msg":"中共避不過十月一<br />\n大家到時一齊去賀賀佢"},{"pid":"aba159190daf916a41630f3e55ebf561c808c751","tid":1528472,"uid":114032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T14:17:57.000Z","msg":"最後嗰段完全係中南海嘅內心描寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e660f8daeff1187285fea1176acc5c782e918a6","tid":1528472,"uid":199590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T16:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46279577c225344